name: Area 51 Escape (Canceled)
blurb: Your spaceship had crash landed in Roswell, NM in 1947 and you have been held captive ever since. Now, YOU must make an Area 51 Escape.

rewards.reward: PRIVATE * We truly appreciate your support for the game.  We have some great desktop wallpaper that we created based upon "Area 51 Escape" to show our thanks.

PRIVATE FIRST CLASS * You will receive the item listed in the PRIVATE rewards section, PLUS, you will receive a free copy of "Area 51 Escape" when it is released on your choice of platforms available.
SPECIALIST * You will receive everything listed in the PRIVATE FIRST CLASS rewards section, PLUS, an exclusive copy of the cheats and secret codes to find all the answers in the game.
CORPORAL * You will receive everything listed in the SPECIALIST rewards section, PLUS, a digital download of the soundtrack to the game.
SERGEANT * You will receive everything in the CORPORAL rewards section, PLUS, Your name in the credits under "Supporter".
STAFF SERGEANT * You will receive everything in the SERGEANT section, PLUS, have your name listed on a locker in the barracks section of Area 51.
SERGEANT FIRST CLASS * You will receive everything in the STAFF SERGEANT section, PLUS, your photograph will be placed somewhere in Area 51.
MASTER SERGEANT * You will receive everything in the SERGEANT FIRST CLASS section, PLUS, you will receive an exclusive "Area 51 Escape" T-shirt.
FIRST SERGEANT * You will receive everything in the MASTER SERGEANT section, PLUS, a digital book, including private videos of the entire development process of "Area 51 Escape".

SERGEANT MAJOR *  You will receive everything in the FIRST SERGEANT section, PLUS, we will create one warehouse object of your choice and design and place it somewhere within Area 51.  You will also receive a sealed map of its location just in case you can't find it... but you would have to break the seal to read the location. AND you will have your name listed in the credits of the game as "Sergeant Major" supporter.

COMMAND SERGEANT MAJOR *  You will receive everything in the SERGEANT MAJOR section, PLUS, an official 1947 Newspaper Reprint! The Roswell Incident \u2013 Souvenir reproductions of the front page articles from July 8th & 9th, 1947. \u201dRAAF Captures Flying Saucer On Ranch in Roswell Region\u201d Full Articles! AND you will have your name listed in the credits of the game as "Command Sergeant Major" supporter.

SERGEANT MAJOR OF THE ARMY *  You will receive everything in the COMMAND SERGEANT MAJOR section, PLUS, an exclusive, limited edition, tin reproduction of the "Warning" sign near the Area 51 base. AND you will have your name listed in the credits of the game as "Sergeant Major or the Army" supporter.

HEAD OF THE CIA * You will receive everything that has been listed so far. If you are the type of person that likes to have a hand in the design of a video game, than this choice is for you!  With the help of one of our graphic artists, you will have the opportunity to design and create one of the rooms or buildings in the game.  This room or building will be either below or above ground, depending on what you prefer and/or what is available. This building or room will have your name one it and you will receive a Certificate of Creation as part of the video game.  AND you will have your name listed in the credits of the game as "Vice President" supporter.

COMMANDER IN CHIEF / PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA * You will receive everything in the HEAD OF THE CIA section, PLUS,  your name will be listed in the opening of the game as a Co-Executive Producer AND you will have your name listed in the credits of the game as "Commander In Chief" supporter.
